Package org.opengis.parameter

Class ParameterNotFoundException

  • Object
    • Throwable
      • Exception
        • RuntimeException
          • IllegalArgumentException
            • ParameterNotFoundException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class ParameterNotFoundException
extends IllegalArgumentException
    Thrown by parameter groups (value and descriptor) when a parameter is requested but not found in that group. This exception is typically thrown by the following methods:
    • ParameterDescriptorGroup.descriptor(String)
    • ParameterValueGroup.parameter(String)
    • ParameterValueGroup.groups(String)
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    InvalidParameterNameException, Serialized Form
